Hysteria shook her com. Something was definitely wrong with it. Oh 
well. Hysteria sat down and sighed, suddenly a static filled message 
came over her com. It appeared to be from Kluster. So, he wanted her 
to report to landing bay 1, did he? She may as well, not like she had 
anything better to do:

"On my way."

Hysteria transformed and ran down several corridors before arriving
at 
landing bay 1. She maximized and walked in, locating Zardus on the
far 
side of the bay:

"You wanted me for somethin'?"
